WEBVTT

00:00:01.247 --> 00:00:06.360
Svet je prepun razdornih rasprava,

00:00:06.884 --> 00:00:08.757
konflikata,

00:00:08.781 --> 00:00:10.594
lažnih vesti,

00:00:10.618 --> 00:00:12.204
žrtava,

00:00:13.146 --> 00:00:18.187
iskorišćavanja, predrasuda,
netrpeljivosti, okrivljavanja, vikanja

00:00:18.871 --> 00:00:21.794
i suženog opsega pažnje.

00:00:22.859 --> 00:00:28.048
Ponekad se čini da smo osuđeni
da zauzimamo stranu,

00:00:28.072 --> 00:00:30.334
da budemo zaglavljeni u eho-komorama